ust%20not%20transmit%20any%20worms%20or%20viruses%20or%20any%20code%20of%20a%20destructive%20nature.%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cli%3E%20You%20must%20not%2C%20in%20the%20use%20of%20YTMND%2C%20violate%20any%20laws%20in%20your%20jurisdiction(including%20but%20not%20limited%20to%20copyright%20laws).%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cli%3E%20You%20must%20not%20use%20YTMND%20as%20a%20method%20of%20harassment%20or%20to%20disclose%20the%20personal%20information%20of%20yourself%20or%20others.%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cli%3E%20You%20must%20not%20attempt%20to%20access%20YTMND%20in%20an%20automated%20way%2C%20with%20scripting%20or%20%22bots%22%20to%20create%20sites%2C%20make%20votes%2C%20post%20comments%20or%20any%20other%20action%20which%20requires%20you%20to%20be%20logged%20in.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cli%3E%20Any%20attempt%20to%20%22game%20the%20system%22%2C%20such%20as%20using%20multiple%20accounts%20to%20alter%20site%20scores%20or%20comment%20scores%20will%20result%20in%20the%20immediate%20termination%20to%20any%20accounts%20with%20access%20history%20originating%20from%20IP%20and%20email%20address.%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cli%3E%20Having%20alternate%20accounts%20will%20be%20permitted%20so%20long%20as%20you%20do%20not%20use%20your%20alternate%20accounts%20to%20vote%20or%20harass%20users.%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%20%20%3C%2Fol%3E%0A%0A%20%20%3Cp%3EViolation%20of%20any%20of%20these%20agreements%20will%20result%20in%20the%20termination%20of%20your%20YTMND.com%20account.%0A%20%20%20%20While%20YTMND.com%20prohibits%20such%20conduct%20and%20content%20on%20its%20site%2C%20you%20understand%20and%20agree%20that%20YTMND%0A%20%20%20%20cannot%20be%20responsible%20for%20the%20Content%20posted%20on%20its%20web%20site%20and%20you%20nonetheless%20may%20be%20exposed%20to%20such%20materials%20and%20that%20you%20use%20the%20YTMND.com%20service%20at%20your%20own%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%20%20%3Ch2%3EGeneral%20Conditions%3C%2Fh2%3E%0A%0A%20%20%3Cul%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cli%3E%20We%20reserve%20the%20rig